library(tidyverse)
library(sjmisc)
library(haven)
library(kableExtra)




df_lapop_chile <- readRDS("lapop_chile_220824.rds")




histograma <- df_lapop_chile %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = q2)) +
  geom_histogram()

histograma





df_lapop_chile %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = q2)) +
  geom_histogram() +
  facet_grid(~year) +
  theme_minimal()
